{"tid":2300050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★廢老又贏！輪候公屋現金津貼---非長者1人申請者不屬計劃對象","createTime":"2020-11-25T08:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T13:31:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a90fc9330eaefc99640ed6257474c6304226a0b","tid":2300050,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"計劃對象是「一般申請住戶」，即是2人或以上家庭和長者1人申請者，換言之，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>非長者1人申請者不屬計劃對象</strong></span>。消息人士解釋，當局目標是在3年內讓「一般申請住戶」上樓，但非長者1人申請者輪候方式採用計分制，並無3年上樓的指標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561888-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561888-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=3b666b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561888-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dcc05f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561888-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a04c3d84860f6c948bbae80676cc211f6ed537a7","tid":2300050,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANGr2GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGr2GX.png&h=017d56af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46b734d120b9174ba800d55a943470301b29a77a","tid":2300050,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"廢老=吸食後生血液既寄生蟲"},{"pid":"f270f5eedc9d4c169a90258753ce694a7e58d063","tid":2300050,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwT2W9K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwT2W9K.jpg&h=04f0ac36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40a492ad1f06ab9c50ed59e6142fa1511fd0f2